<I>i.e.</I> six zodiacal signs rise by day, six by night.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note16" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Aetna/text*.html#ref16
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
